The paper discusses a technique for lifting resource consumption information from compiled to source code, which is a topic related to programming languages (cs.PL) and computer architecture (cs.AR). The proposed approach involves indexing cost labels with loop iterations, which is a topic related to software engineering (cs.SE), systems and control (cs.SY), and loop optimization (cs.LOOP).
